snippet.title: Might&Magic Duel of Champions - Gamescom Trailer [UK]
snippet.description:
Play the game on: http://www.mm-doc.com. 

Might & Magic Duel of Champions, a new online free-to-play card game in the Might and Magic Universe. A closed beta of the game is available now and players can request a beta key by visiting 
http://www.mm-doc.com
